/news/music/watch-johnny-marr-perform-solo-and-smiths-classics-with-30-piece-orchestra-at-manchester-homecoming-show-3556175">在曼彻斯特返校演出中与 30 人的管弦乐团</a>合作演奏了一系列独奏和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯的</a>经典作品。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/johnny-marr-live-in-manchester-pictures-setlist-3556065"><em>《NME》</em>在对该节目的四星级评论中表示：</a> “马尔在过去十年中的四张个人专辑中的歌曲占据了主导地位，但不可避免的是，过去的选择剪辑最能有效地唤醒观众。”</p><p>最近，他还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-charlatans">The Charlatans</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tim-burgess">Tim Burgess</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-charlatans-tim-burgess-join-johnny-marr-for-electronics-getting-away-with-it-3489180">在哈利法克斯的 Piece Hall</a>翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/electronic">Electronic</a>的《Getting Away With It》。</p><p>此次表演是最近与 Marr 进行的一系列舞台合作中的最新一次，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-johnny-marr-perform-a-smiths-classic-with-gaz-coombes-3482572">Gaz Coombes 也曾在 2023 年 Lakefest 上与 Gaz Coombes 一起登台</a>表演史密斯乐队的经典作品《There Is A Light That Never Goes Out》。</p><p>马尔最近还发行了“Spirit Power”，这是他作为独奏艺术家的第一张精选专辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CxZ95g5KDro/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-rad